\n                <dd>- -v tp help specify the voice to say the command\r\n                </dd>\r\n                <dd><img class=\"command\" src=\"../assets/commands-08.png\"></dd>\r\n\r\n                <br>\r\n\r\n                <dt>whoami</dt>\r\n                <dd>Shows the user name of the current user </dd>\r\n                <dd><img class=\"command\" src=\"../assets/commands-09.png\"></dd>\r\n\r\n                <br>\r\n\r\n                <dt>Man (command)</dt>\r\n                <dd>View the manual pages (or view detailed information) on a specific command</dd>\r\n                <dd>For example type \"man ls\" and it will show you a manual for how to use the command</dd>\r\n                <dd>- Press q to quit</dd>\r\n                <dd><img class=\"command\" src=\"../assets/commands-10.png\"></dd>\r\n\r\n            </dl>\r\n\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>', '<style>\r\n.wrapper {\r\n    min-height: 20vh;\r\n    /*padding: 2vh 3em; */\r\n    color: hsl(0, 100%, 100%);\r\n    font-size: 130%;\r\n    padding: 3em;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.wrapper a {\r\n    color: #4CAF50\r\n}\r\n\r\nh1 {\r\n    line-height: 1.5;\r\n    display: inline;\r\n    background-image: linear-gradient(transparent 50%,\r\n            #2BAE66FF 50%,\r\n            #2BAE66FF 85%,\r\n            transparent 85%,\r\n            transparent 85%);\r\n    background-repeat: no-repeat;\r\n    background-size: 0% 100%;\r\n    animation: animatedBackground 2s cubic-bezier(0.645, 0.045, 0.355, 1) 0.5s forwards;\r\n}\r\n\r\n@keyframes animatedBackground {\r\n    to {\r\n        background-size: 100% 100%;\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n.centr {\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n    position: relative;\r\n}\r\n\r\n@import url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans);\r\n\r\n/*Page styles*/\r\n\r\n\r\n.boxes {\r\n    margin: auto;\r\n    padding: 3em;\r\n    /*    background: #484848;*/\r\n    font-family: \'Fira Code\', monospace;\r\n    border: 0.1875em solid;\r\n    border-im